<h1 id="toc0"><span>Crash's flashy art-dash</span></h1>
<p><strong>Hey guys! Welcome to my art hub!</strong> Here is where I will post all my SCP related art.<br />
I hope to use this to draw more often and improve more, so I hope this shines through.</p>
<script type="text/javascript" src="http://d3g0gp89917ko0.cloudfront.net/v--3e3a6f7dbcc9/common--javascript/yahooui/tabview-min.js">
</script>
<div id="wiki-tabview-0a6f9582c06c04bea1dcfb5f6a44bbb4" class="yui-navset">
<ul class="yui-nav">
<li class="selected"><a href="javascript:;"><em>Fanart of singular SCPs</em></a></li>
<li><a href="javascript:;"><em>Commission by GreenWolf</em></a></li>
<li><a href="javascript:;"><em>NonSCP horror art</em></a></li>
</ul>
<div class="yui-content">
<div id="wiki-tab-0-0">
<p>This is for all Fanart focussing on singular articles and/or my favourite aspects of them.</p>
<p>I will try to do mostly newer SCP's/SCP's I have not seen a lot of fanart of, although I won't rule out the occasional &quot;classic&quot;. Overall it is just based on my favourites though. :D</p>
<p><strong>By the way</strong>: If you have any suggestions for underappreciated SCPs or are an author that would like to have some art I'd be very happy to take a look at them and see what I can do! :D</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Taboo</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&nbsp;Just&nbsp;repeat&nbsp;the&nbsp;last&nbsp;syllable&nbsp;of&nbsp;any&nbsp;name&nbsp;you&nbsp;use&nbsp;one&nbsp;additional&nbsp;time&nbsp;for&nbsp;everytime&nbsp;you&nbsp;use&nbsp;it!&nbsp;Tabooboo&nbsp;Taboobooboo&nbsp;Tabooboobooboo.&nbsp;</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>To start things off with number <strong>1</strong>, here is an SCP that I think about on an at least weekly basis: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppersghost" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1553042); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1553042&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1584240612" alt="PeppersGhost" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1553042)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppersghost" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1553042); return false;">PeppersGhost</a></span>'s <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/taboo">Woods Beyond Name</a>.</p>
<img src="https://i.imgur.com/GKqTfOt.jpg" width="600px" alt="GKqTfOt.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">4104</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&nbsp;What&nbsp;will&nbsp;be&nbsp;left&nbsp;after&nbsp;he&nbsp;did&nbsp;whatever&nbsp;it&nbsp;is&nbsp;he&nbsp;wants&nbsp;to&nbsp;do?</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Number <strong>2</strong> is <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/krysalems" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4327863); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4327863&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1584240612" alt="KrySalems" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4327863)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/krysalems" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4327863); return false;">KrySalems</a></span>' <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-4104">&quot;He’s lying to you all.&quot;</a>. A cold and eerie story about nothing.</p>
<img src="https://i.imgur.com/SPmasSr.gif" width="600px" alt="SPmasSr.gif" class="image" />
<p>This is my first time really using a gif in an artistic way so I hope it came out well.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">4444</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&nbsp;Tbh&nbsp;the&nbsp;only&nbsp;thing&nbsp;I&nbsp;knew&nbsp;about&nbsp;Gore&nbsp;before&nbsp;this&nbsp;was&nbsp;the&nbsp;Southpark&nbsp;depiction.&nbsp;</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>And here goes number <strong>3</strong>! <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1888434); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1888434&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1584240612" alt="djkaktus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1888434)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1888434); return false;">djkaktus</a></span>' <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-4444">Bush vs Gore</a>!</p>
<img src="https://i.imgur.com/0LZY6tl.jpg" width="600px" alt="0LZY6tl.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">3596</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Number <strong>4</strong> is a cute story about superheroes and Saturday mornings: <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-3596">SCP-3596</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/iamtheooga" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3942052); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3942052&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1584240612" alt="IAmTheOoga" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3942052)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/iamtheooga" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3942052); return false;">IAmTheOoga</a></span>!</p>
<img src="https://i.imgur.com/X5z78LS.jpg" width="600px" alt="X5z78LS.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">4005</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">It's&nbsp;an&nbsp;extra&nbsp;dimensional&nbsp;anglerfish&nbsp;ain't&nbsp;it?</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Number <strong>5</strong> is <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tufto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3337265); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3337265&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1584240612" alt="Tufto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3337265)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tufto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3337265); return false;">Tufto</a></span>'s <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-4005">SCP-4005</a>. This one was especially interesting to me because it was described as an optimistic, &quot;happy-end&quot;-kinda story when to me it only grew more and more uncomfortable and scary.</p>
<img src="https://i.imgur.com/QWLNhd2.jpg" width="600px" alt="QWLNhd2.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Super&nbsp;Secret&nbsp;shit</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">What&nbsp;it&nbsp;actually&nbsp;is</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/6ZI3xpa.jpg" width="600px" alt="6ZI3xpa.jpg" class="image" />
<p>(screenshot is from me and my friend's server)</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">4051</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Poor&nbsp;Rainer.</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Number <strong>6</strong> is special to me because my first idea for an SCP, before joining the site, was: &quot;a guy that could produce anything out of the pockets of any coats he wore&quot;. And this is basically that concept but realized in proportions and with a complexity, I would have never been able to. It is <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-4051">SCP-4051</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4665703); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4665703&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1584240612" alt="Nagiros" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4665703)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4665703); return false;">Nagiros</a></span>.</p>
<img src="https://i.imgur.com/cjCPgLh.png" width="600px" alt="cjCPgLh.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">3165</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&nbsp;Who&nbsp;needs&nbsp;foxy&nbsp;girls&nbsp;when&nbsp;you&nbsp;can&nbsp;have&nbsp;wolfy&nbsp;ones?</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Number <strong>7</strong> took the scary murder monster and made it not only interesting but also kinda cute. I wanted to give her some (misshapen) lipstick but it only ever looked like blood. :(<br />
And yeah I can do colour too! :P This is <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-3165">Dog Teeth</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dog-teeth" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3116447); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3116447&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1584240612" alt="Dog Teeth" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3116447)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dog-teeth" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3116447); return false;">Dog Teeth</a></span>!</p>
<img src="https://i.imgur.com/NfICRgd.png" width="600px" alt="NfICRgd.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">4377</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">People&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;people&nbsp;god!</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Number <strong>8</strong> is <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-4377">Fight! Fight for the Man of the People!</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/maliceaforethought" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2902864); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2902864&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1584240612" alt="MaliceAforethought" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2902864)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/maliceaforethought" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2902864); return false;">MaliceAforethought</a></span>! Funny, weird and fucking annoying to draw! (Drawn in barely an hour so excuse the sketchiness) :D (and before you ask, yes it is exactly 48 people if you count them right.)</p>
<img src="https://i.imgur.com/hkAfkQe.png" width="600px" alt="hkAfkQe.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">4966</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Munchies!</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Number <strong>9</strong> is <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-4966">Tubbioca: Devourer of Souls, Consumer of Secrets, Lord of Munchies</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/deadly-bread" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3988532); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3988532&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1584240612" alt="Deadly Bread" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3988532)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/deadly-bread" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3988532); return false;">Deadly Bread</a></span>! We got Minecraft Tubb, goop Tubb, scrunched Tubb, ball Tubb, flat Tubb, weird Tubb, <em>s</em>e<em>x</em>x<em>y</em> Tubb, long cat Tubb and finally: normal Tubb.</p>
<img src="https://i.imgur.com/QNRZbkh.png" width="600px" alt="QNRZbkh.png" class="image" />
<p>But wait, there's more!</p>
<hr />
<p>We got Ouroborous tubby, baseball tubby, infinite tubby, angel tubby, even sexier tubby, looooooooooooong tubby, cat tubby, anime tubby, 999 tubby, boot tubby (good bed) and finally knot tubby!</p>
<img src="https://i.imgur.com/XPd4XD2.png" width="600px" alt="XPd4XD2.png" class="image" />
<p>But wait! There's <em>more</em>!</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: line-through;">-</span>-</p>
<p>Can you guess all the GoIs?</p>
<img src="https://i.imgur.com/9cbQR5m.png" width="600px" alt="9cbQR5m.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">3785</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Look&nbsp;up&nbsp;at&nbsp;the&nbsp;sky</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Number <strong>10</strong> is <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-3785">Jasper's Hill</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1888434); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1888434&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1584240612" alt="djkaktus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1888434)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1888434); return false;">djkaktus</a></span>! Starts as a slasher movie, ends with space octopus. What more could you want?</p>
<img src="https://i.imgur.com/HEeZFOg.png" width="600px" alt="HEeZFOg.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">3540</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Queereaper</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Number <strong>11</strong> is <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-3540">Don't queer the reaper!</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mayday" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(412838); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=412838&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1584240612" alt="Mayday" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=412838)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mayday" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(412838); return false;">Mayday</a></span>!<br />
I started drawing this and wanted to do them, standing in their door with a bowl of sweets, but then it hit me. American Gothic. This is one of those rare moments where I am just really proud to have come up with this because that title and the parody is just way too perfect.</p>
<img src="https://i.imgur.com/Jap8ctB.png" width="600px" alt="Jap8ctB.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">4137</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Like&nbsp;a&nbsp;sledgehammer&nbsp;through&nbsp;your&nbsp;skull</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
